doc.field: The Effect of Beta-2 Adrenergic Receptor Genetic Variants on Vasopressor Requirements in Surgery Patients: A Meta-analysis.,Fungal shpenoidal sinusitis with osteomyelitis is rare in young immunocompetent patients. We present a case of a presumed fungal sphenoidal sinusitis presenting with second and sixth cranial nerve involvement which resolved well with systemic anti-fungal treatment.
